		server containers other than tom cat
		this adds other and exclusion tag removes tomcat as shown in line 26 to 31
		<dependency>
			<groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
			<artifactId>spring-boot-starter-undertow</artifactId>
		</dependency>-->
